show.description: Betrayed by his sworn brother Kush, Luv — a fallen martial artist with no memory — rises from the streets to reclaim his true identity as the rightful leader. In a world of deadly rivalries, Luv, Emma, and Mr. Roy fight to restore honor against the corrupt forces led by Kush and Yuvaan.
